data.description: Upgraded Single Story Home In Spring Mountain Ranch With Views of the Hills and City Lights.  Contemporary and Open Floorplan Features 4 Bedrooms, 3 Baths, Den and Gourmet Kitchen Connected To Large Family Room and Dining Area.  Kitchen Features Include: Large Island With Room For Bar Stools; Quartz Countertops; Lots of Upgraded Cabinets & Walk In Pantry With Custom Shelves For All Your Storage Needs; 3 Good Sized Bedrooms; Primary Bedroom Has En Suite Bathroom With Separate Soaking Tub and Shower and Walk in Closet With Custom Shelves; Indoor Laundry With Direct Access To Garage;  Upgrades Include Leased Solar System (@$65/mo with FULL MAINTENANCE) Providing for Very Low Energy Costs; Smart Keyless Entry; Automated Blinds Throughout Most of The Home; Tankless Water Heater; Smart Garage Opener System; Front Yard Features Drought Resistance Landscaping;  Don't Miss The Opportunity On This Home Located In A Serene Atmosphere of Unique Neighborhood Setting With Miles Of Walking Trails and NO HOA.  Conveniently Located To UCR, Loma Linda Hospital, VA Hospital And Easy Access To Freeways.
